{"tid":676160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家係咪以為大公文匯係一個普通親共傳媒黎?","createTime":"2018-05-24T07:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T07:06:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f35452dd398e072f5a97925bb2e152610f1253","tid":676160,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"係英治年代長期被政治部緊密關注既物體, 大家真係以為佢地只係普通親共傳媒咁簡單？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要我們把掌握敵情的任務交給他們，就是說把情報網撒下去，敵人的一舉一動都能反映上來。同時為了使鬥爭合法化，一切情况都集中到文匯報，我們安排新聞支部的書記金堯如坐鎮文匯報，把收集到的情况反映給我，我坐鎮中國銀行，經過分析，然後以報館記者的身分打電話給港英政府 。（吳荻舟《從化口述記錄》）</span></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/2416/歷史補遺﹕消失的檔案&mdash;&mdash;吳荻舟和他的時代\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F2416%2F%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%BA%EF%B9%95%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%90%B3%E8%8D%BB%E8%88%9F%E5%92%8C%E4%BB%96%E7%9A%84%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3&d=C6%2FwMpxvgzXTcJaCSL%2FEcb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5bbf836c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/2416/歷史補遺﹕消失的檔案&mdash;&mdash;吳荻舟和他的時代</a>"},{"pid":"942eb7908805732b9cf76f02e25837c06b6345f5","tid":676160,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"大家真係以為大公文匯既「記者」<br />\n<br />\n真係普通既記者？"},{"pid":"d5716f4279eb3bc4a4549b1bc01aa5793d6fcbe3","tid":676160,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T07:05:02.000Z","msg":"鍾庭耀係如何看既?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140513/18718663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140513%2F18718663&d=C6%2FwMpxvgzXTcJaCSL%2FEcb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0e62d5e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140513%2F18718663&h=8eff098c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140513/18718663</a><br />\n<br />\n《大公報》昨日頭條報道鍾庭耀「瘋狂駕駛」，稱記者於40日內5次目擊鍾庭耀違反交通規例，形容他「將四線雙程行車的薄扶林道當作『私家飆車場』」，又訪問私家偵探，引述其形容鍾的駕駛方法類似特工的反跟蹤駕駛方法；又稱特工不一定發現有人跟蹤才使出反跟蹤手段，可能習慣性地懷疑遭人跟蹤。<br />\n<br />\n對於《大公報》相關報道，鍾庭耀拒絕回應。而與鍾庭耀一樣佔中活動參與度甚高的學民思潮召集人黃之鋒，日前稱被來歷不名男子跟蹤數小時，昨日被傳媒拍得旺角雨中浪漫攬女。"},{"pid":"4cd518481632c839b1346a42513534072b00b9bf","tid":676160,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T07:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkupress.hku.hk/pro/cvr/226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkupress.hku.hk%2Fpro%2Fcvr%2F226.jpg&h=158abde6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}